body:
The command prints the following output if it succeeds.

```json
{
  "ok": 1,
  "cursor": {
    "firstBatch": [
      {
        "name": "<store-name>",
        "provider": "s3",
        "region": "<region-name>",
        "bucket": "<bucket-name>",
        "delimiter": "<delimiter>",
        "prefix": "<prefix>"
      },
      {
        "name": "<store-name>",
        "provider": "atlas",
        "clusterName": "<cluster-name>",
        "projectId": "<project-id>"
      },
      ...
    ],
    "id": NumberLong(0),
    "ns": "<database>.$cmd.listStores"
  }
}
```
